50|$|Derivatives of {{salicylanilide}} have {{a variety}} of pharmacological uses. Chlorinated derivatives including niclosamide, oxyclozanide, and rafoxanide are used as anthelmintics, especially as flukicides. Brominated derivatives including dibromsalan, metabromsalan, and <b>tribromsalan</b> are used as disinfectants with antibacterial and antifungal activities.|$|E

